    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<h2>Using Google's Gson</h2>\n\n<p>Why not use Google's Gson as mentioned in <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/22033974/5320562\">here</a>?</p>\n\n<p>Very straight forward and did the job for me:</p>\n\n<pre><code>HashMap&lt;String,String&gt; map = new Gson().fromJson( yourJsonString, new TypeToken&lt;HashMap&lt;String, String&gt;&gt;(){}.getType());\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2418810,
      "reputation" : 894,
      "user_id" : 2112296,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 13,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/54e9a81d7fd071990bca746f78424efa?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "NameNotFoundException",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2112296/namenotfoundexception"
    },
